<i>Display time and date in you dock with the <span color='#0000FF'>clock applet</span> !</i>
 2 view are available : numeric and analogic, based on <i>Cairo-Clock</i>.
 It can detach itself to be the perfect clone of CairoClock.
 It can warn you with alarms,
  can display a calendar (left/middle click to show/hide it),
  and allow you to setup time and date.
 Left click to show/hide the calendar,
  middle click to stop an alarm and/or hide dialogs.